Within the [[Grand Army of the Republic/Legends|Grand Army of the Republic]], "'''Red Zero'''" was the request for immediate evacuation. This emergency command was used when encountering a disaster of some kind which must be very serious. A Red Zero always had top priority and would be transmitted to all ships and vessels within reach as well as to the operational HQ.

367 days after the [[First Battle of Geonosis/Legends|First Battle of Geonosis]], [[Omega Squad]] boarded a disguised Separatist transport during a TIOPS mission. One of the legitimate freighters traveling in the three ship convoy fired on the TIV, unaware that it was a Republic special forces ship. This caused a serious hull breach and forced Omega to signal a "Red Zero". [[Captain/Legends|Captain]] [[Ordo Skirata|Ordo]] in Coruscant HQ received the message and relayed it to fleet command; RAS ''[[Fearless]]'', [[Majestic (Acclamator-class)|''Majestic'']] and [[Delta Squad/Legends|Delta Squad]] (on board a captured [[Neimoidian/Legends|Neimoidian]] vessel) responded to this request. Eventually, Omega was saved by [[Delta Squad/Legends|Delta Squad]], who reached their position first, and ''Fearless'', who saved them from a Separatist attack ship.

